The `messages` variable passes an array of dictionaries with different roles in the conversation delineated by system, user, and assistant. The system message can be used to prime the model by including context or instructions on how the model should respond.The GPT-35-Turbo & GPT-4 how-to guide provides an in-depth introduction into the options for communicating with these new models.
